The paper discusses deep neural networks and their compression, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of auto-encoders and feature maps suggests that the paper may also fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of the student network, which suggests that it may also fall under neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) as these categories often deal with performance evaluation.
